  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Requirement: Melee, Blocking Weapon property You are skilled in the art of defense, protecting yourself and your nearby allies.</p><p> You gain the following benefits.</p><p> • When you take the Dodge action on your turn, you also gain advantage on Strength saving throws.</p><p> • When an allied creature within 5 feet of you would take damage as the result of an attack, you can spend your reaction to interpose and intercept it.</p><p> The triggering attack now is compared to your AC as you become its target.</p><p> The allied creature cannot be targeted by the same creature until the end of the current turn, with you instead becoming the target each time an attempted attack would happen.</p><p></p>",
